# MoodJournal Mobile

Abandoned Expo SDK 57 portfolio client. API lives in `moodjournal` on GitHub.

- Mood UI is local-only; there is no journal API.
- Use Expo Router navigation helpers — never import `@react-navigation/*` in app code.
- Prefer `npm start` (LAN) or `npm run start:offline` for device work.
- Resolve API URL via `config/appConfig.ts` / `EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL` (port 8080).
- No project-scoped MCP required.
